g.text: Starts the proccess of registering a new clinical analysis laboratory
[for how many test types the lab operates]
Shows list with test types and asks to select the ones the lab operates
Requests data (name, address, phoneNumber, TIN, labID)
cal = registerClinicalAnalysisLaboratory(name, address, phoneNumber, TIN, labID)
Shows the data and requests a confirmation
Adds clinical analysis laboratory to list and informs the success of the operation
